# CLIENT ID command tests - Get client connection ID
@name CLIENT-ID
@group connection
@since 5.0.0

=== TEST: CLIENT ID returns integer
RUN:
CLIENT ID
EXPECT:
(match) \\d+

=== TEST: CLIENT ID unique per connection
RUN:
CLIENT ID
EXPECT:
(match) \\d+

=== TEST: CLIENT ID positive integer
RUN:
CLIENT ID
EXPECT:
(match) [1-9]\\d*

=== TEST: CLIENT ID consistent
RUN:
CLIENT ID
EXPECT:
(match) \\d+

=== TEST: CLIENT ID no arguments
RUN:
CLIENT ID extra
EXPECT:
(error) ERR wrong number of arguments for 'client|id' command
